pageProduct.name: Qsilica Pro Collagen One A Day 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Qsilica Ceramosides + Antioxidant PRO COLLAGEN One-A-Day Capsules is a convenient, vegan supplement formulated with Ceramosides™ and key ingredients silicon and vitamin C to support skin health and collagen formation.

Warnings

Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

If symptoms persist talk to your health professional.

Do not use if carton seals are missing or broken. Do not use if blister seal is broken.

Store out of reach of children.
 
Store below 25°C.

See base of carton for product expiry date and batch number.

Common Uses

Qsilica Ceramosides + Antioxidant PRO COLLAGEN One-A-Day Capsules contain a patented natural wheat seed extract known as Ceramosides as well as colloidal mineral silica, Acerola Berry and Vitamin C.

Both mineral silica and vitamin C (ascorbic acid) maintain skin health and support collagen formation. Mineral silica supports the health of collagen while Vitamin C is an antioxidant helping to reduce free radicals formed in the body.

Ingredients

Active ingredients per capsule:

Silica – colloidal anhydrous…………...............................130 mg
(Equiv. to Silicon 60 mg)
Triticum aestivum (wheat) extract equiv. to dry seed endo.............................. 20.01 g
(from Ceramosides 30 mg)
Malpighia glabra (Acerola) extract equiv. to dry fruit……..…………….....................500 mg
Calcium ascorbate dihydrate…….................................49.67 mg
(Equiv. to Ascorbic acid 45 mg)

Directions

Adults: Take one capsule per day with a glass of water.
